msgstr "El paquete contiene un tipo de recurso no permitido."

msgid "The editor can search and insert ARASAAC pictograms. ARASAAC pictograms are licensed CC BY-NC-SA (owner: Government of Aragón; author: Sergio Palao): attribution is mandatory and commercial use is not permitted by that license."
